,"classes":[]},{"id":37113,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/12\/refuge-in-allah-toilet\/","url_meta":{"origin":13739,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bathrooms: Refuge in Allah before relieving oneself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 12, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Arqam reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, these washrooms are inhabited by jinn. When one of you enters his place of relief, let him say: I seek refuge in Allah from foul and noxious things.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15494,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dua-traveling-at-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":13739,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for traveling at night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: Whenever the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out on a journey, he would say by nightfall, \u201cO earth, my Lord and your Lord is Allah. I seek refuge in Him from your evil, from the evil you contain, from the evil created\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15316,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/dhikr-regret-remembering-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":13739,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhi